ons, what was the highest home attendance registered during the storied campaign?\n\n17. Seek out the cultural gem of Glasgow where entertainment thrives — when did this magnificent theatre first open its majestic doors?\n\n18. How high in elevation does this grand venue rise above sea level, showcasing performances that captivate all hearts?\n\n19. Uncover the star rating bestowed upon this theatre by grateful patrons — a reflection of their appreciation.\n\n20. Combine the altitude of the theatre with the adoration expressed in its rating to reveal a new figure for your journey.\n\n21. Once more, examine the height of this cultural cornerstone to gather yet another important datum.\n\n22. Now, turn your attention to a town known for its planned creation — what is the population residing in this engineered community?\n\n23. Find out how high above sea level this town is positioned, a testament to its landscaped planning.\n\n24. Nearby, how many churches can be counted that offer spiritual sanctuary to the residents?\n\n25. Take the elevation of this town and add it to the count of churches, yielding another significant number for your quest.\n\n26. Reinvestigate that height, as it holds further secrets to uncover and guide your next steps.\n\n27. Determine the largest prime factor from the population of the planned town — a numerical mystery awaiting your discovery.\n\n28. In your wandering, discover many parks near an exotic location — how many green oases can you find around this destination? \n\n29. Finally, compute the result of (your answer from clue 1 + the figure from clue 4 + the value from clue 6) % 10 to reveal a digital treasure on your adventure.",
